data.description: PRICE REDUCED TO SELL!!  Welcome Home to the highly sought-after East Lake Village! This Key West style single-family home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Boasting 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and 2 car garage, this home provides ample space for your family. The large bedrooms ensure everyone has their own sanctuary, while the convenient upstairs laundry makes chores a breeze. The main bedroom features a walk-in closet, providing plenty of storage for all your belongings. But the perks don't end there! East Lake Village offers a plethora of amenities with a community pool, walking trails and kids' playgrounds. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful single-family home in East Lake Village. Close to Beaches, Shopping and Hospitals!
